
  # Crestron HTML5 UI Builder

  This is a code bundle for Crestron HTML5 UI Builder. The original project is available at https://www.figma.com/design/DZS8qkw1PObViNIKooai4Y/Crestron-HTML5-UI-Builder.

  ## Running the code

  Run `npm i` to install the dependencies.

  Run `npm run dev` to start the development server.
